    "text": [
        "Dear sir,",
        "I am William, I am writing this letter to inform you about missing of my certificate. Which I collected yesterday from the institution. While I was on my route to back home. I was encounter heavy rain with fast wind. Unfortunately, I was riding the bike and certificate I was placed on top cover of the bike. Due to heavy rain, forces to stop the bike at many places. I am not sure about where it can be lost.",
        "This certificate is significant for me to begin my career. In the campus selection I have already selected by one of the best software company. Now they requested me to send the certificate for processing my employment. They have allotted me very short time to join, without this certificate that will be not possible. So it is my humble request you to re-issue another certificate as soon as early. Whatever it will cost I am ready to pay.",
        "Tomorrow afternoon I will visit the college. So I can collect the certificate. Please give the instructions to your staff to prepare it. Please consider it as quite serious matter and Speed up the process.",
